title: Old Testament Hebrew Vocabulary: Learn on the Go
description:
Old Testament Hebrew Vocabulary: Learn on the Go
by: Jonathan T. Pennington - Unabridged (2003)

   ISBN-13: 978-0310254928
   Format: MP3 (64k) [with PDF booklet]
   Length: 02:11:24

Description:

In this set of two audio CDs [MP3s here], Jonathan T. Pennington reads all the Hebrew words that occur twenty times or more in the Old Testament in descending order of frequency, followed by an English definition.

These two CDs with a booklet enable a person who is taking biblical Hebrew to work on, by ear as well as through the eyes, all vocabulary words that occur in the Old Testament 20 times or more and all the names of people in the Old Testament that occur 100 times or more
